title: Too Famous for Bitcoin!
description:
A hilarious catch up with Jillian in a fan favorite “too famous segment” - for moving, crypto currency, and her recent segment on Live with Kelly and Ryan. Plus, email questions on TRX, exogenous ketones, vitamin/supplement quality, speeding up your metabolism at 65, how social drinking affects weight loss, and more!
